<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/56726944-christine-mathieu"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1609920953i/56726944._UY100_CR24,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
