        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1953188594" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11317842977472860966">One of the most chilling characters in literature I have ever encountered. Tom Ripley is all the more horrifying because of his total lack of empathy; someone who has looked into the abyss and thinks nothing of pushing others into it while laughing. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

