      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/1817520-the-talented-mr-ripley">Quotes from The Talented Mr. ...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Anticipation! It occurred to him that his anticipation was more pleasant to him than the experiencing.&rdquo;</span>
